OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1772287406
OL,3,CChurch leaders did not act on Bishop
OL,4,Csexual assault allegations - review
OL,6,FSenior clerics in the Church in Wales
OL,7,Fknew a vicar was accused of sexually
OL,8,Fassaulting a child, but did not act
OL,9,Fand still allowed him to be promoted
OL,10,Fto Bishop of Brecon and Swansea,
OL,11,Faccording to a critical review.
OL,13,FAn independent review commissioned by
OL,14,Fthe Church found that several members
OL,15,Fdid not act and did not follow up on
OL,16,Fconcerns when an allegation of sexual
OL,17,Fassault was made against the former
OL,18,FBishop, Anthony Pierce, in 1993.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/18
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1772287406
OL,3,CChurch leaders did not act on Bishop
OL,4,Csexual assault allegations - review
OL,6,FThe review says the Church's handling
OL,7,Fof Pierce's case at the time was
OL,8,F"wholly inappropriate and inadequate".
OL,10,FAmong those referenced in the review
OL,11,Fare several Archbishops of Wales,
OL,12,Fincluding John Davies, Barry Morgan
OL,13,Fand Rowan Williams, the former
OL,14,FArchbishop of Canterbury.
OL,16,FThose most seriously criticised in the
OL,17,F131-page document include Bishop Dewi
OL,18,FBridges, Archdeacon Brian James,
OL,19,FArchdeacon Wynford Rees and former
OL,20,FArchbishop of Wales Alwyn Rice Jones,
OL,21,Fall of whom have since died.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/18
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1772287406
OL,3,CChurch leaders did not act on Bishop
OL,4,Csexual assault allegations - review
OL,6,FThe allegations against Pierce only
OL,7,Fcame to light last year when he was
OL,8,Fjailed after admitting to sexually
OL,9,Fassaulting a child under the age of 16
OL,10,Fwhile working as a parish priest at
OL,11,FHoly Cross Church in Swansea.
OL,13,FThe Church in Wales says, "This
OL,14,Fcatalogue of failures can only be a
OL,15,Fsource of shame for the Church and
OL,16,Fwill have caused further trauma to
OL,17,Fabuse victims and their families.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/18
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1772287406
OL,3,CChurch leaders did not act on Bishop
OL,4,Csexual assault allegations - review
OL,6,F"While the safeguarding processes of
OL,7,Fthe Church in Wales have improved
OL,8,Fimmeasurably since the periods covered
OL,9,Fby the Review, there is no room for
OL,10,Fcomplacency."
OL,12,FAccording to the independent review,
OL,13,FPierce is alleged to have sexually
OL,14,Fassaulted a 15 or 16-year-old boy in
OL,15,For around 1990.
OL,17,FThe boy's mother reported the assault
OL,18,Fto Bishop Dewi Bridges and Archdeacon
OL,19,FWynford Rees three years later.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/18
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1772287406
OL,3,CChurch leaders did not act on Bishop
OL,4,Csexual assault allegations - review
OL,6,FDuring a subsequent meeting with Dewi
OL,7,FBridges, Pierce offered to resign. The
OL,8,Fresignation was refused, and the
OL,9,Fallegations were later described as
OL,10,F"unsubstantiated". In 1995, Dewi
OL,11,FBridges promoted Pierce to Archdeacon
OL,12,Fof Gower.
OL,14,FIn 1999, Pierce was elected as Bishop
OL,15,Fof Swansea and Brecon. At this point,
OL,16,Fthe review says more evidence
OL,17,Fsurfaced. Archbishop Alwyn Rice Jones
OL,18,Fand Archdeacon Brian James received a
OL,19,Fformal letter of complaint from the 16-
OL,20,Fyear-old's mother.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/18
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
