SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1772287406
OL,3,CChurch leaders did not act on Bishop
OL,4,Csexual assault allegations - review
OL,6,FA 30-page handwritten document written
OL,7,Fby a friend of Pierce's detailing an
OL,8,Fadmission was also hand-delivered to
OL,9,FAlwyn Rice Jones in February 1999.
OL,11,FAlwyn Rice Jones did nothing with
OL,12,Fthese documents. He regarded it as "a
OL,13,Fbit of a hiccup and as evidence of
OL,14,Fhomosexuality, not paedophilia and
OL,15,Fthat this was a blip and it should
OL,16,Fjust be put to one side".
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/18
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1772287406
OL,3,CChurch leaders did not act on Bishop
OL,4,Csexual assault allegations - review
OL,6,FThe review found that former
OL,7,FArchbishop of Canterbury, Rowan
OL,8,FWilliams, was given a copy of the
OL,9,Fhandwritten report containing
OL,10,Finformation about Anthony Pierce when
OL,11,Fhe became Archbishop of Wales in 2000.
OL,13,FAccording to the review, Alwyn Rice
OL,14,FJones had given Rowan Williams the
OL,15,F1999 report "for safekeeping," and
OL,16,Fthat "should any further questions
OL,17,Farise about (Pierce's) history, the
OL,18,Fcontents might help."
OL,26,@yD@MpmyD@Vpn
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/18
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1772287406
OL,3,CChurch leaders did not act on Bishop
OL,4,Csexual assault allegations - review
OL,6,FBishop Williams told the review he
OL,7,Fdidn't read the report at the time and
OL,8,Fwasn't aware of its contents. Although
OL,9,Fhe took the report with him to Lambeth
OL,10,Fas part of his personal papers when he
OL,11,Fbecame Archbishop of Canterbury.
OL,13,FIt was not passed on to his successor
OL,14,Fas Archbishop of Wales, Barry Morgan,
OL,15,Fmeaning key safeguarding information
OL,16,Fwas not available in Wales for nearly
OL,17,F10 years.
OL,19,FThe review says the former Archbishop
OL,20,Fdid not know the contents of the
OL,21,Fhandwritten report.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/18
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1772287406
OL,3,CChurch leaders did not act on Bishop
OL,4,Csexual assault allegations - review
OL,6,FRowan Williams told ITV News he "had
OL,7,Fno indication at all of its containing
OL,8,Fa serious admission of guilt". He
OL,9,Fsaid: "I accept that it was an error
OL,10,Fto take it with me to Lambeth when I
OL,11,Fmoved, rather than immediately passing
OL,12,Fit to my successor or checking that he
OL,13,Fhad access to it."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/18
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
