PN,46610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1772287406
OL,3,CChurch leaders did not act on Bishop
OL,4,Csexual assault allegations - review
OL,6,FThe former Archbishop of Canterbury
OL,7,Fadded: "I am very conscious that
OL,8,F(Anthony Pierce's) victims and their
OL,9,Ffamilies will feel that the processes
OL,10,Fof the Church did not adequately
OL,11,Fprotect them at that time, and am very
OL,12,Fsorry indeed for any ways in which I
OL,13,Fcontributed to this, however
OL,14,Finadvertently."
OL,16,FThe former Archbishop of Wales, John
OL,17,FDavies, was also criticised in the
OL,18,Findependent review. He became the
OL,19,FBishop of Swansea and Brecon in 2008
OL,20,Fand the Archbishop in 2017.
OL,26,@pD@ApmpD@Rpn
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/18
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
