PN,46611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1772287406
OL,3,CChurch leaders did not act on Bishop
OL,4,Csexual assault allegations - review
OL,6,FThe review found that, in 2009, he
OL,7,Fknew there had been a safeguarding
OL,8,Fallegation made against Pierce in
OL,9,F1993, and 1999. He knew Pierce had
OL,10,Fadmitted to doing something
OL,11,F"improper", but stated he was
OL,12,F"satisfied" the matter had been dealt
OL,13,Fwith.
OL,15,FJohn Davies didn't initially refer the
OL,16,Fallegation to an ongoing historic
OL,17,Fcases review and delayed referring it
OL,18,Ffor a year. A year later, Bishop
OL,19,FDavies referred allegations, and
OL,20,FPierce had his 'permission to
OL,21,Fofficiate' removed.
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@JO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G11/18
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
