OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1772287406
OL,3,CChurch leaders did not act on Bishop
OL,4,Csexual assault allegations - review
OL,6,FSeventeen years after the allegation
OL,7,Fwas first made, the Church referred
OL,8,Fthe allegation to the police.
OL,10,FHowever, South Wales Police were
OL,11,Funable to investigate because the
OL,12,Falleged victim had died. Last year,
OL,13,FSouth Wales Police told ITV News:
OL,14,F"Sadly, in this specific case, the
OL,15,Fvictim had passed away in 2010 when
OL,16,Fallegations were made of abuse taking
OL,17,Fplace in 1993 (...) Therefore we are
OL,18,Fnot able to progress the
OL,19,Finvestigation".
OL,26,@yD@OpmyD@Spn{D@NO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G12/18
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46613
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1772287406
OL,3,CChurch leaders did not act on Bishop
OL,4,Csexual assault allegations - review
OL,6,FIn 2011, Bishop Davies reinstated
OL,7,FPierce's permissions, "without seeking
OL,8,Fprior advice from a safeguarding
OL,9,Fprofessional". The reviewer says John
OL,10,FDavies was "very reluctant to take any
OL,11,Fresponsibility" for this decision.
OL,13,FThe review continues, "the language of
OL,14,Fthe letter suggested that (Pierce) had
OL,15,Fnot been involved in any misconduct,
OL,16,Fwhen the probability of an indecent
OL,17,Fact having taken place between a 50
OL,18,Fyear old man and a 15/16 year old
OL,19,Fchild was still very high."
OL,26,@vD@[pmvD@bpn
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G13/18
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46614
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1772287406
OL,3,CChurch leaders did not act on Bishop
OL,4,Csexual assault allegations - review
OL,6,FIt also accuses John Davies of using
OL,7,Fan inappropriate tone in further
OL,8,Fcorrespondence with Pierce.
OL,10,FBishop Davies told ITV News, "I
OL,11,Freceived no advice or guidance from
OL,12,Feither its Safeguarding professionals
OL,13,For anyone else at the Church in Wales
OL,14,Fto take any further action once the
OL,15,Fpolice and ISA had made their
OL,16,Fdecisions nor did I know that this
OL,17,Foption was open to me. I considered it
OL,18,Freasonable to reinstate the
OL,19,Fpermission."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G14/18
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46615
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1772287406
OL,3,CChurch leaders did not act on Bishop
OL,4,Csexual assault allegations - review
OL,6,FHe added, "I would unreservedly
OL,7,Fexpress my utter abhorrence of what
OL,8,FPierce did, and my personal sorrow for
OL,9,Fthe suffering which has been caused.
OL,11,F"I am certain that today's
OL,12,Fsafeguarding procedures and processes
OL,13,Fare significantly more robust than in
OL,14,Fthe past."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G15/18
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46616
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1772287406
OL,3,CChurch leaders did not act on Bishop
OL,4,Csexual assault allegations - review
OL,6,FThe review concludes that because
OL,7,Fthese historical weaknesses were so
OL,8,Fsevere, the Church must implement
OL,9,Fmandatory safeguarding vetting for all
OL,10,Ffuture bishop and archdeacon
OL,11,Fcandidates before they are even
OL,12,Fnominated.
OL,14,FThe current Archbishop of Wales,
OL,15,FCherry Vann, told ITV News: "The
OL,16,Fwelfare of the victims of sexual abuse
OL,17,Fmust always be our paramount concern,
OL,18,Fand we offer our most heartfelt
OL,19,Fapologies to those who have been
OL,20,Ffailed by the Church in the past.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G16/18
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46617
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1772287406
OL,3,CChurch leaders did not act on Bishop
OL,4,Csexual assault allegations - review
OL,6,F"The Review shows in painful detail
OL,7,Fthe missed opportunities, the harmful
OL,8,Fassumptions and the inadequate
OL,9,Fprocesses which characterised the
OL,10,FChurch's response to these allegations
OL,11,Fof abuse for far too long.
OL,13,F"This catalogue of failures can only
OL,14,Fbe a source of shame for the Church
OL,15,Fand will have caused further trauma to
OL,16,Fabuse victims and their families.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G17/18
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46618
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1772287406
OL,3,CChurch leaders did not act on Bishop
OL,4,Csexual assault allegations - review
OL,6,F"While the safeguarding processes of
OL,7,Fthe Church in Wales have improved
OL,8,Fimmeasurably since the periods covered
OL,9,Fby the Review, there is no room for
OL,10,Fcomplacency, and we are committed to
OL,11,Fensuring that our processes always
OL,12,Ffollow current best practice."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G18/18
